### WhatsApp Bot API Test Client
@baseUrl = http://195.20.17.83:7879
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:7879

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get WhatsApp Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### List All Sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions

### Send Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Content-Type: application/json

